snippet.title: Amber Lawrence - Happy Ever After [Official Video]
snippet.description:
The beautiful single from Amber Lawrence's album 'Happy Ever After'.

www.amberlawrence.com.au

-----

Lyrics:
So many stories told, about how it’s supposed to go
I want it to end so well, picture perfect, how could I tell
Do you remember that boy with the smile so sweet,
used to walk to school down Evan’s Street
Played a trick and his life ended instantly

We’re all banging on about ‘Happy Ever After’
Give up the moment to see what else we can find
Running through life trying to get there faster
I’ll take my ‘Happy Ever After’, one day at a time

So many songs I’ve heard, pretending that life don’t hurt
When I’m lying under stars with the man I love
Even if we’re doing it tough, for me I know, it’s enough

Wishing, Waiting, Hoping, Praying, ‘cause we’re all insane
Wishing, Waiting, Hoping, Praying, oh yeah…

-----

Written by:
Amber Lawrence - Kayla Bonnici - Nathan Eshman - Sarah Aarons
